node.text:
KNOW-HOW
Grand Siècle was evolved in 1959 from the unique know-how of the House of Laurent-Perrier, with the philosophy of the art of assemblage: the assemblage of vintages, grape varieties and Crus.
The @coutellerie_ceccaldi know-how is manifold: the processing of steel, the carving of the finest woods, and the processing of horn. A craftsman's art, a unique know-how.
#GrandSiecle #RecreatingThePerfectYear

NEW LIMITED-EDITION: LAURENT-PERRIER CUVÉE ROSÉ BUTTERFLY
Bold creativity.
More than 50 years after its launching, Laurent-Perrier Cuvée Rosé still amazes us with its enchanting notes and intense red fruits aromas. Its unique and reusable champagne serving ritual has been reinvented for the 4th consecutive year.
#LaurentPerrier #ChosenByTheBest
